# Dir2Path

`dir2path` is a simple utility that appends the current directory to your shells `$PATH`. Currently supports ZSH and BASH.

## Installation

installation via pip

```shell
$ pip install dir2path
```

## Usage

```shell
$ cd ~/my/local/bin/folder
$ dir2path
```

